data.description: VA ASSUMABLE LOAN AT 3.125%  Motivated Seller! All Financing Options Accepted   Go Show Property is Vacant and Ready for Move In!   Beautiful and Spacious 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath End-Unit located 4 miles from  the Quantico gate and right off the exit from I-95 and Route 1. Freshly painted two stories Condo. Located on the 2nd level is the Luxury owner's suite with large walk-in closet and bathroom. Upstairs also includes 2 additional bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, washer and dryer hookup, a second living area and balcony. Downstairs is well lit with tons of natural lighting throughout the living room, kitchen and dining area . Also featured on the main level is a half bathroom and access to a one-car garage. This impeccable residence is located near great dining and shopping options, making it a desirable home for anyone looking to live in a well kept community. Don't miss the opportunity to make this home your own!  ***SELLER OFFERING TO COVER  THE FIRST 6 MONTHS OF CONDO FEES***  Water and Trash Included
